Body:
And [yet,] they have a sign [of Our power to create and to
			resurrect] in the lifeless earth which We make alive, and out of
			which We bring forth grain, whereof they may eat;

And [they have a sign in] the sun: it runs in an orbit of its
			own<span class='fn'>19</span> - [and] that is laid down by the will of the
			Almighty, the All-Knowing;

[And they are unaware that] nothing awaits them beyond a single
			blast [of God's punishment],<span class='fn'>27</span> which will overtake them
			while they are still arguing [against resurrection]:
